    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Actor component: manages one Tryll server-side agent. Attach to any Actor; Blueprint users bind to the delegates and call <ref refid="class_u_tryll_agent_component_1ad8c21935bebe0e779cde76a8931b5aff" kindref="member">SendMessage()</ref>.</para>
<para>Graph resolution order:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>WorkflowAsset (if set) — designer-authored data asset in the Content Browser.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>InlineGraphDescription — set programmatically in C++ or edited in the Details panel.</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>The component auto-creates an agent once the session is ready (if bAutoCreateOnConnect) — it queues until OnConfigureSessionComplete if it spawns before the session is configured. It auto-destroys the agent on EndPlay. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
